    Ant Task to bootstrap Processors. Creates and invokes BootstrapProcessorTask.Processors found on the class path. 
    <BootstrapProcessorTask basedir="File" classname="String" classpathref="Reference" description="String" destdir="File" srcdir="Path" taskname="String">
  <classpath .../>
  <src .../>
</BootstrapProcessorTask>
